WOMAN:
 <i>Manuel?</i>

00:24.100 --> 00:25.067
 <i>Can you hear me?</i>

00:27.784 --> 00:31.084
Manuel wake up
Huh?

00:32.116 --> 00:34.284
What?
What are you doing?

00:34.318 --> 00:38.117
What, what, what are...
what are you talking about?

00:38.151 --> 00:41.551
Geez, Manny,
are you all right?

00:41.585 --> 00:44.184
