00:51.951 --> 00:55.117
 <i>Our dreams reveal us</i>
 <i>to ourselves.</i>

00:55.151 --> 00:56.251
 <i>The people we are.</i>

00:56.284 --> 00:57.850
Don't just shoot,
you gotta aim it.

00:57.884 --> 01:00.017
So when that site is in
the middle of the clown's mouth,

01:00.051 --> 01:02.451
then you shoot.
Okay, Daddy.

01:02.484 --> 01:05.184
 <i>The people we'd like to be.</i>

01:05.218 --> 01:07.551
Whoo! Yeah!

01:07.585 --> 01:09.384
You don't need much.

01:09.418 --> 01:11.551
Just a little push.

01:12.618 --> 01:15.051
Oh, hole in two!

01:15.084 --> 01:16.084
Hey!

01:16.117 --> 01:17.717
Ah, come on, boy!

01:20.984 --> 01:22.318
You guys have fun?

01:22.351 --> 01:24.218
Oh... sure did.

01:24.251 --> 01:25.218
(grunting):
All right.

01:29.618 --> 01:30.817
Here's your deposit.

01:30.850 --> 01:33.284
A lot of people tell me
the game's even more fun

01:33.318 --> 01:35.451
when they bring their own kid,
rather than renting one.

01:35.484 --> 01:37.418
I know. I heard that.

01:37.451 --> 01:39.618
You know how
to get one?

01:39.651 --> 01:41.451
I know people.

01:49.951 --> 01:51.184
(grunting):
Yeah.

01:54.318 --> 01:57.351
(sighing):
Wait a second, will you?

01:57.384 --> 01:58.884
What are you talking about--

01:58.917 --> 02:00.318
"heads blown off"?

02:05.284 --> 02:07.284
Mm... do me a favor,
look around.

02:07.318 --> 02:11.351
Sometimes... a kid will hide
under the bed, in a closet.

02:13.984 --> 02:15.351
All dead.

02:15.384 --> 02:19.951
No, I have no idea
where the mayor is.

02:19.984 --> 02:21.251
It's 5:52 in the morning.

02:21.284 --> 02:23.784
I'm guessing
that he's at home, asleep.

02:23.817 --> 02:26.850
Wait a second,
give me an address.

02:26.884 --> 02:28.884
How many children?

02:32.251 --> 02:34.551
No, don't move anything,
just lock it down.

02:34.585 --> 02:36.318
I'm maybe 35 minutes away.

02:36.351 --> 02:38.750
I'll be right down there.

02:46.784 --> 02:49.318
