MAN:
Speak English.

04:03.545 --> 04:06.211
You want English?

04:06.245 --> 04:08.845
Why'd you come to Indonesia?

04:08.879 --> 04:10.145
Go home to America.

04:14.111 --> 04:15.512
Where are you going?

04:15.545 --> 04:16.644
I'm going
to the airport.

04:16.678 --> 04:18.043
I'm going home.

04:18.077 --> 04:19.978
(scoffs)
I feel
like going home.

04:20.011 --> 04:21.978
You can't do that.

04:22.011 --> 04:25.111
You're intoxicated.

04:25.145 --> 04:26.378
Do you even have a ticket?

04:28.545 --> 04:32.944
Besides...
it's early in the morning.

04:32.978 --> 04:35.978
It's not time for traveling.

04:36.011 --> 04:39.845
It's time to make love.

04:39.879 --> 04:41.545
Keep the change.

05:19.378 --> 05:20.579
What's the matter?

05:20.612 --> 05:22.245
What's going on?

05:22.278 --> 05:24.978
A dream?
Ugh, yeah.

05:27.145 --> 05:29.545
You want to talk
about it?

05:29.579 --> 05:30.878
I don't know.

05:30.911 --> 05:35.212
I'm not sure there's anything
to talk about.

05:35.245 --> 05:36.945
Oh, wow.

05:36.978 --> 05:38.512
Well, that's a first.

05:42.111 --> 05:46.345
I mean,
it took place in Indonesia.

05:46.378 --> 05:49.011
I don't know anyone
in Indonesia.

05:50.545 --> 05:51.744
You would've
liked it, though.

05:51.778 --> 05:53.612
There was a naked
girl in it.

05:59.178 --> 06:01.545
This is weird.

06:01.579 --> 06:03.345
I just had the
exact same dream.

06:03.378 --> 06:05.445
Oh, really.

06:05.478 --> 06:06.778
Truly.

06:06.811 --> 06:11.945
Was there a guy in your dream
who got his head chopped off?

06:11.978 --> 06:13.778
No.

06:13.811 --> 06:15.711
I just had the
naked girl part.

06:15.744 --> 06:17.945
I see.

06:17.978 --> 06:19.412
You had a guy...

06:23.811 --> 06:26.378
Well, I hope you're happy.

06:26.412 --> 06:28.145
Now I'm afraid to
go back to sleep

06:28.178 --> 06:29.312
and finish the dream.

06:29.345 --> 06:32.078
Yeah, well,
welcome to my world.

